title: The 6 Most Important Decisions to Make in Your Life
itunes:title: The 6 Most Important Decisions to Make in Your Life
description:
You will make many decisions in your life but these are the 6 MOST important ones you will need to make. If you can make the right choices on these decisions, you will have a life far beyond what most people can imagine.
